4. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper discusses channel estimation in a frequency division duplexing (FDD) downlink system, which is a topic closely related to networking and internet architecture. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper discusses channel estimation in a massive MIMO-OFDM system, which is a topic closely related to multimedia communication.
